Cognate with {{cog|stq|Bäie}}, {{cog|vls|beier}}, {{cog|de|Beere}}, {{cog|is|ber}}, {{cog|da|bær}}.

The slang sense “police car” may come from the lights on the vehicles’ roofs.<ref>{{R:GDoS|pos=n|sense=1|id=hm2zbiy}}</ref>

