=====Usage notes=====
Many fruits commonly regarded as berries, such as [[strawberry|strawberries]] and [[raspberry|raspberries]], are not berries in the botanical sense, while many fruits which are berries in the botanical sense are not regarded as berries in common parlance, such as bananas and pumpkins.

